# 🛡️ Module 4: AI Strategy & Governance - Wharton Business School
### *AI Governance, Transparency & Explainable AI (XAI)*

This final module focuses on the institutionalization of AI oversight. As an AI Automation Engineer, I analyze the mechanisms of **Algorithmic Accountability**, the implementation of **Explainable AI (XAI)**, and the design of **Governance Frameworks** that ensure long-term trust and regulatory compliance.

